 OCC:Why not

    Galvatron saw the bot. he seemed to be waiting. "Yopu gave me a great 
gift sir. You allowed me something new. He transformed. He was liquid for a 
second and suddenly he was in robot mode. he had the green jewel on his 
chest. He had a smooth shaped body. Steel wings. His knees could undo and 
show the gun cannons. On his hand there where a single hole on each. They 
could shout about 6 in beams of energy out of them. A gift from enertron. His 
tail was regrown and the wound in his stomach was gone. Enertron was not 
worht his time with his new power. His hands where steel claws as sharp as 
could be. He pointed a finger. "You are no further challenge. I give mercy. 
Your a valent warrior but doomed in this conflict." He spread his wings and 
flew off. He sent a cloud off gas from his feet to hide his departure trail. 
His wings made incredible speed. And the bot had no chance in his condition 
to catch him. He followed the track of his brother. His form was complete. It 
was done.

--part1_f5.66ed26c.278f855d_boundary
